1
00:00:54,640 --> 00:00:56,680
We just want to take our own car.

2
00:00:56,880 --> 00:00:57,560
What are you doing here?

3
00:00:57,560 --> 00:00:58,120
What is going on here?

4
00:00:58,120 --> 00:00:59,250
We just want the car.

5
00:00:59,800 --> 00:01:01,480
You can take the car,

6
00:01:01,720 --> 00:01:03,200
but we can't refund the money.

7
00:01:03,200 --> 00:01:04,760
You can take it to any repair shop

8
00:01:04,760 --> 00:01:05,519
for an inspection.

9
00:01:05,519 --> 00:01:07,520
If you can prove the problem is on us,

10
00:01:07,520 --> 00:01:08,720
we will compensate you tenfold.

11
00:01:08,720 --> 00:01:10,039
Come on. Let's hurry up and get it tested.

12
00:01:10,039 --> 00:01:11,300
Let's go get it tested.

13
00:01:13,080 --> 00:01:15,280
We must make him fully convinced today.

14
00:01:16,960 --> 00:01:18,920
Good thing that guy brought you back.

15
00:01:18,920 --> 00:01:19,880
Otherwise,

16
00:01:20,039 --> 00:01:21,120
I wouldn't know how to live.

17
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:22,920
Don't run around anymore, okay?

18
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,039
Keke.

19
00:01:24,160 --> 00:01:24,890
Shake hands.

20
00:01:25,800 --> 00:01:28,130
So now you know how happy it is to have a dog.

21
00:01:30,920 --> 00:01:32,800
Zhu Keke is quite unlucky

22
00:01:32,840 --> 00:01:34,240
to have such a stupid dad.

23
00:01:35,360 --> 00:01:37,020
What are you muttering about?

24
00:01:39,039 --> 00:01:41,039
Keke, come have some water.

25
00:01:41,240 --> 00:01:42,920
You must be so hot. Come on.

26
00:01:44,680 --> 00:01:45,340
Drink more.

27
00:01:48,360 --> 00:01:51,800
Break up with Tianyu right now.

28
00:01:52,000 --> 00:01:52,560
What?

29
00:01:54,200 --> 00:01:56,240
You're dating your creditor?

30
00:01:56,600 --> 00:01:57,360
No.

31
00:01:57,360 --> 00:01:58,880
We're just... If you hadn't exposed me in public,

32
00:01:58,880 --> 00:01:59,600
about me swapping parts,

33
00:01:59,600 --> 00:02:01,520
everyone in the neighborhood wouldn't have known.

34
00:02:01,520 --> 00:02:02,980
Now my business is ruined.

35
00:02:03,160 --> 00:02:05,420
What good does it do you to ruin our store?

36
00:02:05,480 --> 00:02:06,240
Ruin it?

37
00:02:06,760 --> 00:02:07,440
Su Wan,

38
00:02:07,720 --> 00:02:09,600
what happened to you in the warehouse?

39
00:02:09,600 --> 00:02:11,360
Never mind what happened in the warehouse.

40
00:02:11,360 --> 00:02:13,280
She ruined our business.

41
00:02:13,440 --> 00:02:14,720
I'm asking my sister.

42
00:02:14,880 --> 00:02:16,240
What does it have to do with your warehouse?

43
00:02:16,240 --> 00:02:17,640
Yes, it's your sister.

44
00:02:17,760 --> 00:02:19,079
She ruined our store's business.

45
00:02:19,079 --> 00:02:21,040
I don't care about your store.

46
00:02:21,160 --> 00:02:22,160
I'm asking

47
00:02:22,320 --> 00:02:24,560
what happened between her and her creditor.

48
00:02:24,560 --> 00:02:26,040
Stop. Stop arguing.

49
00:02:26,520 --> 00:02:28,920
Find a way to recover the business within a week.

50
00:02:28,920 --> 00:02:30,640
Cousin, come with me to the store now.

51
00:02:30,640 --> 00:02:31,480
Help them restore their business.

52
00:02:31,480 --> 00:02:32,120
Let me go.

53
00:02:34,040 --> 00:02:34,520
You...

54
00:02:35,680 --> 00:02:36,520
Keke, you...

55
00:02:36,920 --> 00:02:37,200
Wait a minute.

56
00:02:37,200 --> 00:02:39,160
Keke, come here. Don't lose my dog again.

57
00:02:39,160 --> 00:02:39,880
Keke, let's go.

58
00:02:39,880 --> 00:02:40,360
Go.

59
00:02:42,400 --> 00:02:43,920
So what if you're rich?

60
00:02:47,840 --> 00:02:49,640
As long as it solves the problem.

61
00:02:50,560 --> 00:02:51,880
Bai, tell me.

62
00:02:52,079 --> 00:02:53,400
Did you, in the warehouse,

63
00:02:53,400 --> 00:02:54,680
seduce my ignorant, innocent,

64
00:02:54,680 --> 00:02:56,210
and inexperienced cousin?

65
00:02:58,760 --> 00:02:59,480
I...

66
00:03:02,720 --> 00:03:03,760
I can't be bothered to explain it to you.

67
00:03:03,760 --> 00:03:04,240
I...

68
00:03:05,800 --> 00:03:07,400
You have no responsibility and no tolerance.

69
00:03:07,400 --> 00:03:09,480
Even if you don't speak, you can't blame it on my cousin.

70
00:03:09,480 --> 00:03:11,600
All right, that's not the point.

71
00:03:11,800 --> 00:03:12,920
The point is how we can

72
00:03:12,920 --> 00:03:15,450
restore the auto repair shop's business now.

73
00:03:34,920 --> 00:03:35,880
Hello, Senior.

74
00:03:36,320 --> 00:03:37,800
What's the matter?

75
00:03:38,480 --> 00:03:39,200
Su Wan,

76
00:03:39,440 --> 00:03:41,640
I want to ask you out to a movie tomorrow.

77
00:03:42,720 --> 00:03:43,780
No thanks, Senior.

78
00:03:43,880 --> 00:03:45,160
I have other plans tomorrow.

79
00:03:45,160 --> 00:03:46,400
Don't be like this.

80
00:03:46,400 --> 00:03:47,920
You're rejecting me the first time I ask you out.

81
00:03:47,920 --> 00:03:49,880
Don't play hard to get with me.

82
00:03:50,400 --> 00:03:52,200
You know that I like you.

83
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,360
Like?

84
00:03:54,240 --> 00:03:56,160
Are you kidding me, Senior?

85
00:03:56,480 --> 00:03:57,120
It's true.

86
00:03:57,640 --> 00:03:58,720
I really like you.

87
00:03:59,320 --> 00:04:00,360
I want to pursue you.

88
00:04:00,360 --> 00:04:02,520
Sorry, I already like someone.

89
00:04:02,840 --> 00:04:04,800
Stop joking. Don't be shy.

90
00:04:04,880 --> 00:04:06,080
How is that possible?

91
00:04:06,160 --> 00:04:07,400
If you didn't like me,

92
00:04:07,600 --> 00:04:09,200
why would you answer my call?

93
00:04:09,240 --> 00:04:10,040
Besides,

94
00:04:10,680 --> 00:04:13,080
where else can you find a guy better than me?

95
00:04:13,920 --> 00:04:15,960
It can't be that guy Ding Shiyu mentioned, right?

96
00:04:15,960 --> 00:04:17,200
He dresses like that.

97
00:04:17,560 --> 00:04:19,399
How could you be interested in him?

98
00:04:19,399 --> 00:04:21,519
People who don't know would think he's a mechanic.

99
00:04:21,519 --> 00:04:23,200
It's not your place to judge him.

100
00:04:23,200 --> 00:04:25,200
Besides, so what if he is a mechanic?

101
00:04:25,280 --> 00:04:26,610
He really is a mechanic.

102
00:04:26,920 --> 00:04:28,000
So I guessed right.

103
00:04:28,480 --> 00:04:30,140
In what way am I worse than him?

104
00:04:30,360 --> 00:04:33,040
I have money, I have looks, and I have an education.

105
00:04:33,040 --> 00:04:34,680
Any random bracelet I wear

106
00:04:36,400 --> 00:04:37,680
is worth more than

107
00:04:37,880 --> 00:04:39,320
a dozen of his rags.

108
00:04:40,040 --> 00:04:40,920
Then let me tell you,

109
00:04:40,920 --> 00:04:42,120
when it comes to respecting others,

110
00:04:42,120 --> 00:04:43,980
you've already lost completely.

111
00:04:46,840 --> 00:04:47,880
Mechanic.

112
00:04:51,720 --> 00:04:53,800
Free car inspection, 50% off.

113
00:04:55,280 --> 00:04:56,920
Will a poster alone work?

114
00:04:57,400 --> 00:04:59,720
This is a big plan to save the garage.

115
00:05:00,120 --> 00:05:01,450
Whether it works or not,

116
00:05:02,680 --> 00:05:03,680
we have to try.

117
00:05:03,960 --> 00:05:04,640
Yeah.

118
00:05:05,120 --> 00:05:06,560
You do it if you don't like it.

119
00:05:06,560 --> 00:05:07,800
You hooked up with my sister.

120
00:05:07,800 --> 00:05:09,280
You should be secretly happy.

121
00:05:09,280 --> 00:05:10,680
How dare you question it?

122
00:05:11,880 --> 00:05:12,480
Awesome.

123
00:05:18,520 --> 00:05:19,980
Why are you so close to her?

124
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,320
I am her cousin.

125
00:05:21,720 --> 00:05:24,120
Even a cousin doesn't need to be this close.

126
00:05:25,120 --> 00:05:25,720
Be quiet.

127
00:05:25,880 --> 00:05:26,440
Water.

128
00:05:30,680 --> 00:05:31,740
What are you doing?

129
00:05:32,000 --> 00:05:33,159
This is his water.

130
00:05:33,720 --> 00:05:36,040
Wait, did I agree to you two being together?

131
00:05:36,040 --> 00:05:38,100
You're already indirectly kissing.

132
00:05:43,040 --> 00:05:43,640
Chen.

133
00:05:44,600 --> 00:05:45,600
Drink this glass,

134
00:05:46,440 --> 00:05:47,600
and what we discussed last time

135
00:05:47,600 --> 00:05:49,930
about investing in the garage is settled.

136
00:05:53,480 --> 00:05:54,240
Let her do it.

137
00:05:58,280 --> 00:05:58,880
Okay.

138
00:05:58,960 --> 00:06:00,220
Quick, pour the drink.

139
00:06:01,000 --> 00:06:01,680
Hurry up.

140
00:06:04,080 --> 00:06:04,600
Hurry.

141
00:06:16,800 --> 00:06:19,200
Brother Chen, let me propose a toast to you.

142
00:06:21,760 --> 00:06:24,040
Little girl, have a drink with me.

143
00:06:29,280 --> 00:06:30,410
It's just one drink.

144
00:06:31,280 --> 00:06:31,840
Come on.

145
00:06:32,080 --> 00:06:32,940
I'm right here.

146
00:06:42,360 --> 00:06:43,040
Sorry.

147
00:06:43,480 --> 00:06:45,610
I need to go to the restroom. Excuse me.

148
00:06:49,400 --> 00:06:50,200
Brother Chen,

149
00:06:50,760 --> 00:06:52,360
let me propose a toast to you.

150
00:06:53,320 --> 00:06:53,980
Bottoms up.

151
00:06:55,200 --> 00:06:56,400
Boring.

152
00:07:03,400 --> 00:07:04,880
I'll go out to take a call.

153
00:07:05,800 --> 00:07:06,200
Okay.

154
00:07:15,760 --> 00:07:16,640
Hello, Senior.

155
00:07:17,240 --> 00:07:18,640
What's up?

156
00:07:19,400 --> 00:07:20,240
Junior Su Wan,

157
00:07:20,560 --> 00:07:22,220
you finally answered my call.

158
00:07:22,400 --> 00:07:24,260
I am really sorry about last time.

159
00:07:24,400 --> 00:07:26,730
I drank too much and was talking nonsense.

160
00:07:26,880 --> 00:07:28,440
I sincerely apologize to you.

161
00:07:28,440 --> 00:07:30,500
But I also hope you can give me a chance

162
00:07:30,600 --> 00:07:31,800
to get to know me again

163
00:07:32,040 --> 00:07:33,700
and see a different side of me.

164
00:07:34,320 --> 00:07:36,120
I don't think that's necessary.

165
00:07:36,120 --> 00:07:38,200
I made myself very clear last time.

166
00:07:38,480 --> 00:07:39,640
I already have someone I like.

167
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:41,440
I know you have someone you like.

168
00:07:41,800 --> 00:07:43,060
I respect your choice.

169
00:07:43,320 --> 00:07:44,520
At the same time, I also think

170
00:07:44,520 --> 00:07:47,120
that everyone might have the right and chance to be accepted again

171
00:07:47,120 --> 00:07:48,880
and understood.

172
00:07:49,440 --> 00:07:51,600
I'm not forcing you to change your choice.

173
00:07:51,600 --> 00:07:53,400
I just hope you can give me a chance

174
00:07:53,400 --> 00:07:54,530
for us to meet again.

175
00:07:57,480 --> 00:07:58,040
Okay.

176
00:07:58,600 --> 00:07:59,460
How about this,

177
00:08:00,000 --> 00:08:01,460
I'll send you the address.

178
00:08:01,760 --> 00:08:02,480
Great.

179
00:08:02,800 --> 00:08:03,800
Goodbye, Senior.

180
00:08:10,120 --> 00:08:10,800
It seems

181
00:08:11,400 --> 00:08:14,040
Su Wan is starting to sway before my charm.

182
00:08:15,720 --> 00:08:17,520
Now it's up to me.

183
00:08:32,360 --> 00:08:34,490
I have something to do. I need to go out.

184
00:08:35,480 --> 00:08:37,210
But Ding Shiyu just texted that

185
00:08:40,520 --> 00:08:41,650
she'll be here soon.

186
00:08:47,600 --> 00:08:48,130
Brother.

187
00:08:49,200 --> 00:08:49,930
You're here.

188
00:08:51,040 --> 00:08:51,840
Go out first.

189
00:08:55,600 --> 00:08:56,800
You came just in time.

190
00:08:57,480 --> 00:08:58,840
Propose a toast to Mr. Chen.

191
00:08:58,840 --> 00:09:00,880
Our auto repair shop's business will be settled.

192
00:09:00,880 --> 00:09:02,410
I'm really sorry, Mr. Chen.

193
00:09:02,840 --> 00:09:05,170
Our shop is currently facing some issues.

194
00:09:05,360 --> 00:09:06,520
Asking you to invest right now

195
00:09:06,520 --> 00:09:07,960
is really not a good time.

196
00:09:08,800 --> 00:09:10,680
I've already paid the bill for tonight.

197
00:09:10,680 --> 00:09:12,040
My younger sister is still in high school.

198
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:13,640
It's really not suitable for her to stay long,

199
00:09:13,640 --> 00:09:14,680
let alone drink.

200
00:09:14,920 --> 00:09:15,960
As for my younger brother, Yaqi,

201
00:09:15,960 --> 00:09:18,160
if he did anything to offend you tonight,

202
00:09:18,160 --> 00:09:19,290
please forgive him.

203
00:09:19,680 --> 00:09:21,480
I apologize to you on his behalf.

204
00:09:22,240 --> 00:09:24,320
When the shop gets better,

205
00:09:24,760 --> 00:09:27,020
we'll find another chance to cooperate.

206
00:09:28,000 --> 00:09:28,600
Yaqi.

207
00:09:30,440 --> 00:09:31,240
Let's go home.

208
00:09:34,600 --> 00:09:35,800
Stop repairing cars.

209
00:09:38,640 --> 00:09:39,760
Fix your brain.

210
00:09:41,440 --> 00:09:43,440
I've been talking to Mr. Chen for so long.

211
00:09:43,440 --> 00:09:44,840
You can't just reject it.

212
00:09:46,520 --> 00:09:48,250
If you want to leave, you leave.

213
00:09:51,880 --> 00:09:53,600
I'll ask you one last time.

214
00:09:56,520 --> 00:09:57,280
Are you going

215
00:09:58,760 --> 00:09:59,680
or not?

216
00:10:02,520 --> 00:10:04,720
My legs are failing.

217
00:10:05,920 --> 00:10:08,050
You'll have to suffer a bit from now on.

218
00:10:10,160 --> 00:10:10,680
Dad.

219
00:10:11,360 --> 00:10:12,220
Don't say that.

220
00:10:12,760 --> 00:10:14,160
If you hadn't adopted us,

221
00:10:14,240 --> 00:10:16,760
the three of us would have starved to death on the streets.

222
00:10:16,760 --> 00:10:18,840
I plan to quit school.

223
00:10:20,200 --> 00:10:21,000
Rest assured.

224
00:10:21,520 --> 00:10:23,520
I will take good care of this family.

225
00:10:24,480 --> 00:10:26,400
Then I won't go to high school either.

226
00:10:26,400 --> 00:10:28,060
I'll go to a vocational school

227
00:10:28,280 --> 00:10:29,400
to learn auto repair.

228
00:10:29,400 --> 00:10:32,480
That way I can start supporting the family a few years earlier.

229
00:10:32,480 --> 00:10:34,160
Then I won't study either.

230
00:10:34,560 --> 00:10:35,360
No.

231
00:10:36,080 --> 00:10:37,480
You must study hard.

232
00:10:37,960 --> 00:10:40,960
We can't have the whole family be uneducated.
